name: DEVIL’S DEATH PARTY
description:
We all have our inner demons: conflicting feelings, events from the past that haunt us, sadness from people who have fallen out of our way. This piece is a sentimental interpretation of the moment when we are finally able to let go of all that bad weight in search of living the new, in search of peace of mind. When our demons die, we clear our road to happiness.

ITEM SPECS
3840 x 2160 pixels
MP4 file
Softwares used: Blender, Adobe Photoshop, Adobe After Effects
